WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.572
Your responses to complex challenges are heavily dictated by your

00:00:03.572 --> 00:00:07.144
personal values. Authentic leaders exhibit consistency among their values, their

00:00:07.144 --> 00:00:10.716
beliefs, and their actions. When your thoughts, feelings, and behaviors

00:00:10.716 --> 00:00:14.288
align, you are leading with congruence. Congruence is the gravity

00:00:14.288 --> 00:00:17.860
of leadership. It grounds you in your values, provides stability

00:00:17.860 --> 00:00:21.432
for your team, allows others to predict how you will

00:00:21.432 --> 00:00:25.004
act, and fundamentally builds shared trust.
